location.fullValue: Major League Plan, Lake and Lake West, Daybreak

data.description: Gorgeous Townhome in Downtown Daybreak with Amazing Views! Balcony and Windows Face Park and Mountain Views instead of other buildings.  Home has 3 Bedrooms upstairs and an additional Bedroom/Office Space on the first floor! Home includes 9 ft Ceilings, Huge Picture Windows, Quartz Countertops, Tile Backsplash, Laminate Floors, and Pendant and LED Disc Lighting. Smart Home items include:  Keyless Entry, Video Doorbell, SMART Garage Door, a Smart Thermostat!  Home has a 2 Car Garage with Storage, an Electric Outlet for a Car Charger, and a Tankless Water Heater. Home is right across from the Park, Pickleball Court, and PlayGround.  Enjoy all Daybreak Amenities including the Watercourse. Just 5 Minutes away from the new Bees Ballpark coming soon. This Home is a Must See!
